author_ssm: Lauren Kata, with assistance from Archives and Special Collections Student Assistants Stefan Mitikj and Gelila Kebede.
unittitle_ssm: NYU Abu Dhabi Publications and Ephemera
abstract_ssm: The NYU Abu Dhabi Publications and Ephemera collection consists of published bulletins, curricula guides, brochures, research reports, commemencement programs, class yearbooks, events catalogs and calendars, faculty and student journals, and a few commemorative artifacts, which document academic and community life across the NYU Abu Dhabi campus, including research achievements, from 2010 - present.
